## Initialize-Script

Universal PowerShell modules designed to standardize all user notification, error handling, logging, output, and event logging. 

## Contents

There are 4 functions included in Initialize-Script:

* RECORD-EVENT 
* INITIALIZE-LOGFILE
* POPUP-NOTIFICATION
* DEPLOY-DIRECTORIES

## Bundled Functions

DEPLOY-DIRECTORIES : Deploy a series of standardized directories to C:\PowerShell

RECORD-EVENT : Handles all user notification, event handling, error handling, and logging of events for script.

POPUP-NOTIFICATION : Displays a Windows pop-up form to the user

INITIALIZE-LOGFILE : Creates log files using standardized locations and naming conventions.


